<!-- 1인견적 업무 흐름도 -->
<div class="card">
  <div class="card-header">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 flex items-center gap-3">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-500">account_tree</span>
      1인견적 업무 흐름도
    </h2>
    <p class="text-navy-600 mt-1">1인 견적에 의한 수의계약 절차</p>
  </div>

  <div class="p-6">
    <!-- 나라장터 불필요 안내 -->
    <div class="bg-teal-50 border border-teal-300 rounded-xl p-4 mb-4">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-teal-600">verified</span>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-teal-800 mb-1">나라장터 이용 불필요</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-teal-700">1인 견적의 경우 지정정보처리장치(나라장터) 이용 의무가 <strong>면제</strong>됩니다.</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-teal-600 mt-1">근거: 지방계약법 시행령 제30조 제2항 (2인 이상 견적 시에만 의무)</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 1인견적 적용 요건 -->
    <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-xl p-4 mb-6">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-green-600">check_circle</span>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-800 mb-2">1인견적 적용 요건 <span class="text-xs font-normal bg-green-200 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">현행</span></h4>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-3">
              <span class="font-medium text-navy-700">금액 요건</span>
              <p class="text-navy-600">추정가격 <strong>2천만원 이하</strong></p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-3">
              <span class="font-medium text-navy-700">특수 요건</span>
              <p class="text-navy-600">특허, 유일업체, 긴급 등</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 1인견적 가능 사유 -->
    <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-xl p-4 mb-6">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-3">1인견적 가능 사유</h4>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-blue-700">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-blue-500 text-lg">check</span>
          추정가격 2천만원 이하
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-blue-700">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-blue-500 text-lg">check</span>
          특허권 보유 물품
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-blue-700">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-blue-500 text-lg">check</span>
          해당 지역 유일 업체
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-blue-700">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-blue-500 text-lg">check</span>
          긴급한 경우
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-blue-700">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-blue-500 text-lg">check</span>
          농산물·수산물 등 직접 생산자
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-blue-700">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-blue-500 text-lg">check</span>
          2회 이상 견적요청 불응
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 흐름도 -->
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-primary-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">1</div>
        <div class="flex-1 bg-surface-50 rounded-xl p-4 border border-surface-200">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-navy-800 mb-2">1인견적 사유 확인</h4>
          <ul class="text-sm text-navy-600 space-y-1">
            <li>• 추정가격 2천만원 이하 확인</li>
            <li>• 또는 특수 사유 해당 여부 검토</li>
            <li>• 1인견적 사유서 작성 (필요시)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-navy-300 text-2xl">arrow_downward</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-primary-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">2</div>
        <div class="flex-1 bg-surface-50 rounded-xl p-4 border border-surface-200">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-navy-800 mb-2">계약상대자 선정</h4>
          <ul class="text-sm text-navy-600 space-y-1">
            <li>• 적합한 업체 1개사 선정</li>
            <li>• 업체 적격성 검토 (등록증, 실적 등)</li>
            <li>• 견적요청서 발송</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-navy-300 text-2xl">arrow_downward</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-primary-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">3</div>
        <div class="flex-1 bg-surface-50 rounded-xl p-4 border border-surface-200">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-navy-800 mb-2">견적서 접수 및 검토</h4>
          <ul class="text-sm text-navy-600 space-y-1">
            <li>• 견적서 접수</li>
            <li>• 규격 및 가격 적정성 검토</li>
            <li>• 예정가격 이하 여부 확인</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-navy-300 text-2xl">arrow_downward</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 4 -->
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-primary-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">4</div>
        <div class="flex-1 bg-surface-50 rounded-xl p-4 border border-surface-200">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-navy-800 mb-2">계약 체결</h4>
          <ul class="text-sm text-navy-600 space-y-1">
            <li>• 계약서 작성 (소액은 청구서로 갈음 가능)</li>
            <li>• 계약보증금 면제 가능 (2천만원 이하)</li>
            <li>• 계약 체결 및 통보</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="mt-3 bg-amber-50 rounded-lg p-3 text-sm">
            <span class="text-amber-700">💡 추정가격 500만원 이하 시 계약서 생략 가능 (청구서로 갈음)</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-navy-300 text-2xl">arrow_downward</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 5 -->
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-green-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">5</div>
        <div class="flex-1 bg-green-50 rounded-xl p-4 border border-green-200">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-800 mb-2">이행 및 대금 지급</h4>
          <ul class="text-sm text-green-700 space-y-1">
            <li>• 납품/용역 이행</li>
            <li>• 검수 및 검사</li>
            <li>• 대금 지급</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 간소화 절차 안내 -->
    <div class="mt-6 bg-purple-50 border border-purple-200 rounded-xl p-4">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-purple-600">speed</span>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-purple-800 mb-2">간소화 가능 사항</h4>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm">
            <div>
              <span class="font-medium text-purple-700">500만원 이하</span>
              <p class="text-purple-600">→ 계약서 생략 (청구서 갈음)</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="font-medium text-purple-700">2천만원 이하</span>
              <p class="text-purple-600">→ 계약보증금 면제 가능</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
